-- Olympus ex-CEO Woodford to brief media
-- 
-- Thu Jan 5, 2012 6:41pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/01/05/us-woodford-briefing-idUSTRE80429620120105

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Michael Woodford, the ousted CEO of Olympus Corp, said on Friday he will hold a press conference at 0600 GMT to explain the reasons behind his decision to give up his three-month battle to replace the management of the scandal-tainted Japanese endoscope maker. 
 (Reporting By Nobuhiro Kubo; Editing by  Joseph Radford )